<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>C</key>
<lyrics>[C1]
   Thangthat, Halleluijah, Halleluijah
   Bawi vialte, Bawi bik cem
   Halleluijah, Halleluijah
   Jesuh Khrih, ka Bawipa ka Pathian.

[V1]
 Jesuh keimah khamhtu BAwi
 Amah tluk tha ho hmanh umlo
 Cu caah a min thiang cu
 Ka thangthat lai, Vawlei caan
 Dongh hlan tiang.

[V2]
 Dawtnak ruang ah a luang mi
 Thisen sung misual kei caah
 Vailam ah nunnak a pek
 Chim cawk lo, vel ngeihnak
 Dawtnak tling.</lyrics>
<title>THANGTHAT HALLELUIJAH</title>
</song>